/www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14092"><img src="http://users.easystreet.com/korb/images/eq/korby60-corpse-sig.jpg" border="0"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fitzwillowfairbrass>Fitzwillow Fairbrass</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.theviolethour.org/images/Emoticon/boozing.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/03 7:50 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Can a group exp grind in PoS?</span><hr size=1> We usually grind in the desert at the pool with the armadillos.  Single group, we pull whatever comes to hand and get great experience.  Not sure what &quot;really really poor&quot; experience is, random desert mobs suit me just fine since no matter what, it's better than the tier 1 planes.<br>
