Veteran Dethvegi<br>
63rd Warlord <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wulfran>wulfran</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/03 11:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Bees best...</span><hr size=1> My list of preference in POS would be a little different than above...<br>
<br>
1) Frogs in middle cave. Not much for loots aside from diamonds and eth parches, unless you kill them all and then kill Dromok.<br>
<br>
2) Bees in Forest. Drops Wind Lance, storm rider blood, storm rider skins in addition to regular diamonds, copper bars, etc.  Need an ENC or Monk to do with any efficiency.<br>
<br>
3) Desert or Forest giants. Odd drops like midnight mantle, the 35/35 (forget name) and a couple other things that sell for 3-5 Kpp each<br>
