Quellious<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yrocmorf>Yroc Morf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/03 1:01 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.rogers.com/shadowedblade/yroc2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bees best...</span><hr size=1> I like the Dillo camp and surrounding trash mob for relaxing xp (although I'm getting sick of it).<br>
<br>
We do it with a 60 war (~4aa per kill) and a 65 cleric (~2aa per kill) but it was taking a bit too long to make kills .... So <br>
<br>
I decided to add a 55 epic mage on two box for additonal pet DPS .... believe it or not, even when the cleric nuked twice per dillo (~2K dmg) and casted the cleric hammer pet on the mob immidiately, the solo 55 mage was KSing us rarely... one cleric nuke and she KSed us always (rude SoE)...... So<br>
